data.description: Beautifully updated home in the Prairie Meadows Subdivision in Prairie Grove, AR. Step in the front door to the open floor plan featuring a marble fireplace, crown molding, chair rail, LED lighting & more. The dining area features reclaimed wood wains coating. Cherrywood cabinets with under lighting & granite countertops adorn the large kitchen. The huge master suite also features crown molding, granite countertops, reclaimed wood & natural stone. The master bath offers a massive soaking tub & dual walk-in closets. The home is tile & hardwood throughout. A two-speed attic fan was installed complete with gable end fan for air flow & temperature control. The two-car garage has plenty of storage shelving & cabinets as well as a fully decked attic above it for storage. This home is a MUST SEE! Too many beautiful & functional updates to list them all. Seller is offering a $5,000 concession to the Buyer at closing with acceptable offer. Concession to be used at the Buyers discretion.
